data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
PLEASE NOTE: This page should only be accesible to users who have been granted admin priviliges. Do not use any of the features of this page without reason, or your admin status may be revoked.
1. Enter the email address of the user you want to either delete from the system's database, or to promote to an admin.
2. Depending on the desired outcome, select the correct button. If the email address entered in step 1 is a user on the system, then the desired operation will be fulfilled on that user.

data.name: helpAccountText.Text
data.value:
-To add a new entry to the log:
--Input the date of your trip using the date selector. --Then include the name of the zone you fished in, alongside any notes about your trip. --Finally press the "Add Entry" button to add your entry to the log.
-To change your password, type your current and desired new password in the appropriate boxes and press "change password"

data.name: mapHelpText.Text
data.value:
-To move the map, hold down the right mouse button and move the mouse.
-To zoom in and out, scroll the middle mouse wheel.
-Press the "Toggle Map Mode" button to switch between the two map modes.
-Press the "Refresh Map" to update your map with any new zones that have been edited.
-Press the "Quiz" button to access the quiz
